So my born day is tomorrow and I feel extremely blessed to be alive and healthy and walking in my dream. But 10 years ago today my Pops passed away. Still can’t believe it’s been a decade. So since then this time of year is always bitter sweet to me. It truly doesn’t get easier u just get stronger! 

For the longest time I told myself and everyone else ‘I’m Superman’ and didn’t properly deal with the loss until it literally almost killed me. 7 years ago I lost hope and didn’t believe I would be here today but I am simply because GOD GOT ME!! I am a walking testimony that ‘it’s okay to be #Human’ so this song is my reminder to myself and anyone else who needs to hear it!! IT’S OKAY!!!! Tomorrow I hope to touch some lives with this song! Love and Light!! 
🤴🏾👽🎙🎹
